# One resolution per line.
# Format:
#   WxH                          (uses default mask 1FFF — covers common refresh rates)
#   WxHx8,16,32,64=MASK          (full form, hex bitmask)
# Lines starting with # are comments.
#
# Common useful entries for the Odyssey G9 OLED:
# 2304x1440
# 2560x1440
# 3440x1440
